parameters:
Uhyaa! Such smooth skin! I envy it because my skin
is rough and bumpy.

My master hasn't been going on many adventures
lately. It's so boring.
What's wrong? Did you run out of money?

That card game they have at the entertainment
center in the Rein district is so much fun, isn't
it? I want to go again, but I always run out of
money so quickly.

Oh, are you a fellow colleague? This is my house
that I bought with a lot of money. It's nice to
rely on the guild, but it's also fun to work hard
on your own.

Do you know about the dungeon called 'Remi's
Pond'? There's actually a problem happening...

Actually, my best friend Noah got trapped in that
pond... I think she's still alive because there's
air inside the dungeon, but it seems like she
can't get out on her own.

I know, but you need Diving LV2 to go deep into
that dungeon.

As long as you don't get captured by the monster
called Remi that nests there...

If it seems like you can enter, would you be able
to go and help...? The reward will be enticing.
It's better to hurry Leave it to me
I'm a bit busy right now
早いほうがいいわね。任せて
Remi's Pond, huh? Well, can you leave it to me?
Thank you! I'll go to the entrance as well.
Sorry, right now I'm a little preoccupied...

Edda? Ah, I heard she died at Lake Paelis the
other day.
I bought it after it became vacant.

Magical girls don't usually die, but I heard her
magical power completely ran out.
Is it okay to dress like that?

Lolimon has preferences, so it might be efficient
to know them when feeding. If you steadily work on
it, you can increase the ★ even during meals.
ピッキングで解錠する

If you have a \C[2]lock-picking tool\C[0] and a
\C[2]hairpin\C[0], you might be able to challenge
unlocking the door...
盗むレベルによってコモンを変更する
ここで単品アイテム入手
I have a bad feeling about this.
